                    .col-lg-6
                        .bg-yellow.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-left
                                    h4.text-primary <a href="https://github.com/cheststore/cli" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Command Line Interface</a>
                                    p.mb-0.text-black
                                        | Easy to install and use <a href="https://github.com/cheststore/cli" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CLI</a> interface to make all your objects
                                        | manageable and portable regardless of the machine you're on.
